### Gateway Example: Agent Trace Tracking
# Track multi-step AI agent traces end-to-end

POST https://api.costkatana.com/api/gateway/v1/chat/completions
CostKatana-Auth: Bearer YOUR_COSTKATANA_KEY
CostKatana-Target-Url: https://api.openai.com
CostKatana-Project-Id: YOUR_PROJECT_ID
CostKatana-Trace-Id: trace_content_gen_123
CostKatana-Trace-Name: blog-post-generation
CostKatana-Trace-Step: generate-outline
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Create an outline for a blog post about AI."
    }
  ]
}

### Trace Step 2: Generate Content
POST https://api.costkatana.com/api/gateway/v1/chat/completions
CostKatana-Auth: Bearer YOUR_COSTKATANA_KEY
CostKatana-Target-Url: https://api.openai.com
CostKatana-Project-Id: YOUR_PROJECT_ID
CostKatana-Trace-Id: trace_content_gen_123
CostKatana-Trace-Name: blog-post-generation
CostKatana-Trace-Step: generate-content
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Write the blog post based on the outline."
    }
  ]
}

